data.title: Check Out the Tracklist for Mobb Deep's Upcoming Album "The Infamous Mobb Deep"
data.meta_description: The project will include appearances from Nas, Snoop Dogg, Juicy J, and more.
data.text:
Mobb Deep have unveiled the tracklist for their upcoming double-disc album The Infamous Mobb Deep. The first disc includes new material from the veteran Queensbridge duo, who worked with Snoop Dogg, Nas, The LOX, Juicy J, Bun B, Mack Wilds and more on their first album in nearly a decade. Production primarily comes from Havoc, with additional contributions from Illmind, Beat Butcha, and The Alchemist.

The second disc features rare and unreleased material during the time period their 1995 classic album The Infamous was recorded, and is appropriately titled The 1994 Infamous Sessions. Check out both tracklists below. The Infamous Mobb Deep will be released April 1.

1. Taking You Off Here (Produced by Havoc)

2. Say Something (Produced By Illmind)

3. Get Down f/ Snoop Dogg (Produced by Havoc)

4. Dirt (Produced By Illmind)

5. Timeless (Produced By Beat Butcha)

6. All A Dream f/ The LOX (Produced By Ommas Keith)

7. Low f/ Mack Wilds (Produced By Seven Thomas, Havoc, Boi-1da)

8. Murdera (Produced By Illmind)

9. Check the Credits (Produced By Illmind)

10. Gimme All That (Produced by Havoc)

11. Legendary f/ Bun & Juicy J (Produced by Havoc, Boi-1da, The Maven Boys)

12. Lifetime (Produced by The Alchemist)

13. My Block (Produced by Kaytranada)

14. Henny f/ Mack Wilds, Busta Rhymes & French Montana (Produced by Havoc)

15. Conquer (Produced by Havoc)

16. Waterboarding (Produced by Havoc)

17. Get It Forever f/ Nas (Produced by The Alchemist)

The 1994 Infamous Sessions

1. Eye for an Eye f/ Ghostface Killah, Raekwon & Nas (Produced by Mobb Deep)

2. Skit (Produced By Mobb Deep)

3. Get It In Blood (Produced By Mobb Deep)

4. Gimme The Goods (Produced By Mobb Deep)

5. If It’s Alright f/ Big Noyd (Produced By Mobb Deep)

6. Skit Mobb Deep 1995 (Produced By Mobb Deep)

7. Survival of the Fittest (Produced By Mobb Deep)

8. Temperature’s Rising (Produced By Mobb Deep)

9. The Bridge (Produced By Mobb Deep)

10. Skit (Produced By Mobb Deep)

11. The Money (Produced By Mobb Deep)

12. The Money version 2 (Produced By Mobb Deep)

13. We About to Get Hectic (Produced By Mobb Deep)

14. The Infamous (Produced By Mobb Deep)
